   8:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_flash.c ****   *           + Program operations functions
   9:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_flash.c ****   *           + Memory Control functions
